OL,3,CWarning of literacy 'crisis' in Welsh
OL,4,Cschools as 20% of children don't own
OL,5,Cbooks
OL,7,FWales' National Children's Laureates
OL,8,Fare warning of a "crisis" in literacy
OL,9,Fin schools.
OL,11,FNicola Davies, Children's Laureate
OL,12,FWales and Sion Tomos Owen, Bardd Plant
OL,13,FCymru have published an open letter
OL,14,Furging the current and upcoming
OL,15,Fgovernment to take immediate action in
OL,16,Fresponse to the fall in literacy
OL,17,Flevels and reading for pleasure among
OL,18,Fchildren and young people.
