OL,7,FThey said "In spite of the wealth of
OL,8,Fevidence that reading for pleasure is
OL,9,Fa greater indicator of future
OL,11,Facademic success than socio-economic
OL,12,Fstatus, only 1 in 4 children aged 8-18
OL,13,Fin Wales report enjoying reading.
OL,15,F"It is a shocking fact that libraries
OL,16,Fare mandatory in prisons, but not in
OL,17,Fschools; one in four schools in Wales
OL,18,Fdoesn't have any sort of library, let
OL,19,Falone a librarian.
