OL,3,CWarning of literacy 'crisis' in Welsh
OL,4,Cschools as 20% of children don't own
OL,5,Cbooks
OL,7,FLast year an ITV News investigation
OL,8,Fhas found that Welsh primary schools
OL,9,Fare still encouraged to teach reading
OL,10,Fin the wrong way.
OL,12,FIn this approach, commonly referred to
OL,13,Fas "cueing", young children are told
OL,14,Fto use "cues" like pictures or the
OL,15,Fcontext of a sentence if they are
OL,16,Fstuck on an unfamiliar word.
OL,18,FThis technique is based on a flawed
OL,19,Ftheory of how we learn to read, and
OL,20,Fwas discredited by scientists decades
OL,21,Fago.
