OL,5,Cbooks
OL,7,FThe National Literacy Trust is also
OL,8,Fbacking the Laureates' call.
OL,10,FThey have provided books for 6,300
OL,11,Fprimary school children in the last
OL,12,Ffive years and created library spaces
OL,13,Ffor 95 schools in Wales. But they say
OL,14,Fthis only reaches a small proportion
OL,15,Fof the children and schools that need
OL,16,Fbooks and libraries.
