OL,7,FThe Welsh Government says: "Literacy
OL,8,Fis a national priority and we are
OL,9,Falready investing #13.2 million to
OL,10,Fraise literacy standards focused on
OL,11,Fgiving schools consistent national
OL,12,Fsupport rather than shortterm
OL,13,Finitiatives.
OL,15,F"We expect all schools to provide
OL,16,Fbookrich environments and we are
OL,17,Falready seeing improvements in levels
OL,18,Fof attainment. We will continue
OL,19,Fworking hard to raise education
OL,20,Fstandards for all."
